  "text": "GEMCaP and Kattan scores. To evaluate the role of GEMCaP in predicting clinical status, confounding by known disease factors were avoided by selecting cases and controls with comparable baseline features (Supplementary Table S1 ; Table 1 ). The risk classifications according to the fixed, floating, and integrated GEMCaP scores are shown in Supplementary Table S1 and include [CITATION_1] http://www.mskcc.org/mskcc/html/10088.cfm the 5-year postoperative PFP using the Kattan historical nomogram [CITATION_2] . All aCGH log 2 ratios, along with probe information, are provided in Supplementary Table S2 .",
